  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/643970/extras/7bfbba137794a64cbdb83580294fbf97.poster.avif?t=1537362233\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/643970/extras/7bfbba137794a64cbdb83580294fbf97.webm?t=1537362233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/643970/extras/7bfbba137794a64cbdb83580294fbf97.mp4?t=1537362233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Return to Planet X is a close combat FPS in which you will have to smash tons of alien bugs and shoot your way through the secret millitary base located on a distant planet.<br>Our game takes the inspiration in action FPS games like Doom or Half-Life and novels like Starship Troopers.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Laser guns, grenades, explosives and flamethrower<br></li><li> Alien bugs<br></li><li> Explore a world cloaked in mystery and danger<br></li><li> Stunning environments with moody graphics</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/643970/extras/7bfbba137794a64cbdb83580294fbf97.poster.avif?t=1537362233\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/643970/extras/7bfbba137794a64cbdb83580294fbf97.webm?t=1537362233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/643970/extras/7bfbba137794a64cbdb83580294fbf97.mp4?t=1537362233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Return to Planet X is a close combat FPS in which you will have to smash tons of alien bugs and shoot your way through the secret millitary base located on a distant planet.<br>Our game takes the inspiration in action FPS games like Doom or Half-Life and novels like Starship Troopers.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Laser guns, grenades, explosives and flamethrower<br></li><li> Alien bugs<br></li><li> Explore a world cloaked in mystery and danger<br></li><li> Stunning environments with moody graphics</li></ul>",
